Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.39,0:01:26.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:84397,86649}I'm leaving the house\Nunder your care, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.98,0:01:29.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:86983,89193}Okay. Have a nice day!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.53,0:01:39.95,lassie episode,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:95533,99954}{\blur0.5\fad(300,0)\pos(320,280)}Hurry! Save Dr. Hopper
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.13,0:01:53.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:112133,113051}Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.05,0:01:55.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:114052,115303}Good morning, John!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.84,0:01:58.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:116846,118306}Did you make it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.93,0:02:01.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:119932,121267}Good morning, Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.26,0:02:02.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:121267,122060}So?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.31,0:02:03.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:122310,123436}Let me try.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.43,0:02:05.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:123436,125063}Don't be such a glutton.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.06,0:02:09.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:125063,129817}First, I'll give it to your mom, since\Nshe's the one taught me how to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.81,0:02:11.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:129817,131944}So there's nothing for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.94,0:02:15.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:131944,135323}I prepared one for you, too.\NDon't be such a worrywart.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.78,0:02:16.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:135782,136908}Is your mom home?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.90,0:02:18.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:136908,138785}She went to work already.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.78,0:02:19.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:138785,139827}Eh…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.45,0:02:22.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:140453,142830}Relax. We'll ask Lassie to deliver it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.20,0:02:27.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:145208,147085}We're counting on you, Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.04,0:02:34.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:151047,154467}Sandy, we better go as well,\Nor we'll be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.46,0:02:36.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:154467,156844}Ah, wait, wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.98,0:02:48.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:167980,168856}All set.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.38,0:03:25.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:201389,205309}Doctor, I can't take it anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.30,0:03:26.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:205309,206728}You'll live.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.85,0:03:28.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:207854,208813}What's with that look?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.69,0:03:32.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:210690,212442}Let me tell you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.44,0:03:37.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:212442,217071}Treating wounds like yours\Ncouldn't be any more boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.94,0:03:40.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:217947,220116}Maybe you could\Nbreak a bone or two?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.11,0:03:42.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:220116,222618}Please don't even joke like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.61,0:03:44.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:222618,224495}Take care of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.49,0:03:45.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:224495,225788}Next!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.78,0:03:48.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:225788,228332}Doctor, there's something bad\Ngoing on with our daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.33,0:03:49.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:228332,229584}Please, you're our only hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.58,0:03:53.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:229584,233212}Calm down, Hamilton.\NTalk to me. What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.58,0:03:56.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:233588,236507}She's burning up and has chills!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.50,0:03:57.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:236507,237633}Doctor…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.84,0:04:01.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:239844,241345}Put her here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.34,0:04:02.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:241345,242889}Right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.10,0:04:08.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:246100,248102}How does it look, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.10,0:04:09.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:248102,249562}It's nothing serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.56,0:04:11.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:249562,251147}But she's crying so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.43,0:04:14.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:251439,254650}When the parents are worried,\Nthe children get upset as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.94,0:04:19.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:255943,259947}It's just a normal cold. Give her good food\Nand let her sleep comfortably.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.94,0:04:20.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:259947,260656}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.32,0:04:27.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:261324,267163}Moreover, you probably thought she was cold\Nand wrapped her in multiple blankets?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.16,0:04:28.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:267163,268080}That's right…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.08,0:04:30.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:268080,270666}I can't blame you,\Nthat's a typical first reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.66,0:04:33.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:270666,273419}But the body temperature\Nwill only increase further.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.41,0:04:34.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:273419,274670}So that's what caused it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.04,0:04:39.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:275046,279425}For little children, it is particularly\Nimportant to take the fever down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.25,0:04:44.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:280259,284555}Well, now that you know what to do,\Nyou should stay a bit more relaxed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.55,0:04:45.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:284555,285431}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.18,0:04:47.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:286182,287767}Take care of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.76,0:04:51.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:287767,291437}You didn't have to see me off\Nall the way here, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.60,0:04:52.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:291604,292897}Don't be a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.89,0:04:59.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:292897,299445}I didn't come here to see {\i1}you{\i0} off,\Nbut rather this beautiful young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.49,0:05:07.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:304492,307453}A mere dog dares\Nto steal my popularity.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.04,0:05:14.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:312041,314043}– Thank you very much, Doctor!\N– Don't mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.88,0:05:23.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:321884,323553}Come here, show me your tongue.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.18,0:05:27.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:326180,327640}That's a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.64,0:05:30.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:327640,330059}Is my face so scary?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.05,0:05:32.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:330059,332061}I love children, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.06,0:05:34.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:332061,334856}Sometimes the feeling\Nis certainly not mutual.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.14,0:05:37.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:335147,337692}Doctor, I brought you some help.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.87,0:05:50.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:348870,350538}All righty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.95,0:05:52.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:351956,352999}Be careful on your way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.46,0:05:59.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:356460,359797}What do you say?\NWant to hang around with me for today?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.55,0:06:07.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:366554,367805}Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.51,0:06:10.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:368514,370683}She won't bite you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.68,0:06:14.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:370683,374312}She only makes sure\Nyou won't run away, hehe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.98,0:06:23.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:381986,383070}What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.32,0:06:25.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:384322,385156}Is it delicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.15,0:06:26.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:385156,386073}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.61,0:06:29.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:386616,389201}I hope your mom eats it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.20,0:06:31.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:389201,391704}No worries.\NLassie will give it to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.07,0:06:35.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:392079,395416}No, I meant,\NI hope she's going to like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.83,0:06:37.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:395833,397293}She will, she will.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.29,0:06:38.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:397293,398794}Yeah. No doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.79,0:06:44.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:403799,404800}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.80,0:06:46.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:404800,406218}It's delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.21,0:06:47.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:406218,407887}Did you teach her how to make it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.88,0:06:50.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:407887,410723}She is very skilled.\NIt's even better than mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.72,0:06:56.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:410723,416187}That girl, Sandy, has\Na very good sense of taste and smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.43,0:07:00.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:417438,420942}What about your son?\NWhat is John skilled the best at?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.36,0:07:04.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:422360,424946}John? Hard to tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.94,0:07:07.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:424946,427281}It's still too early to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.28,0:07:10.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:427281,430576}But he's been raising Lassie\Nall by himself thus far, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.57,0:07:13.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:430576,433579}He only runs and\Nplays around with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.57,0:07:15.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:433579,435081}But I need to admit,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.08,0:07:19.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:435081,439752}no matter how angry he is with her,\Nhe always takes good care of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.83,0:07:23.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:440836,443464}By the way, Doctor,\Nwhy don't you go fishing today?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.84,0:07:27.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:444840,447718}You have treated\Nso many patients today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.71,0:07:29.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:447718,449845}You deserve a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.84,0:07:31.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:449845,451097}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.09,0:07:32.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:451097,452348}I suppose you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.34,0:07:35.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:452348,455643}All right, then.\NI'll go for just a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.64,0:07:40.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:455643,460356}As always, remember that the siren\Ncan be heard even in the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.35,0:07:42.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:460356,462483}If anything happens,\Njust send me a signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.02,0:07:45.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:463025,465069}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.06,0:07:49.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:465069,469448}Usually you'd be like, "I have done enough!\NNo more patients for today".
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.44,0:07:51.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:469448,471659}Did anything change?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.65,0:07:56.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:471659,476414}For many years, evenings\Nwere the busiest period for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.41,0:07:59.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:476414,479959}I shall take this opportunity\Nto prepare mentally for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.41,0:08:03.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:480418,483713}I'm starting to see him\Nin a new light.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.68,0:08:13.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:492680,493889}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.88,0:08:15.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:493889,495099}You're going home already?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.28,0:08:33.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:512283,513492}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.49,0:08:38.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:513492,518622}I asked you if you'd like to keep me company,\Nbut I didn't mean to go fishing with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.62,0:08:40.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:518622,520124}Oh, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.89,0:08:58.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:536891,538142}What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.14,0:09:01.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:538142,541353}I'm the only one\Nwho knows about this spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.40,0:09:15.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:554408,555993}Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.99,0:09:20.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:555993,560706}What do you think\Nof Greenall Bridge?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.20,0:09:24.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:561207,564251}I love this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.25,0:09:27.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:564251,567671}I traveled to many towns\Nand villages in my life
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.67,0:09:29.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:567671,569298}but this town is the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.29,0:09:31.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:569298,571842}It's so calm and peaceful,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.84,0:09:35.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:571842,575262}and all the townspeople\Nare such hard workers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.35,0:09:45.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:580351,585689}You probably think I'm just\Na worthless old geezer when I'm like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.68,0:09:47.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:585689,587024}But don't be fooled.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.23,0:09:52.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:588234,592530}I run a medical clinic.\NIt is my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.82,0:09:57.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:593823,597451}It's not unusual to see terrible things.\NAccidents, illnesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.45,0:10:01.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:597451,601330}I must take it easy whenever I can\Nto be in top shape when the time comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.16,0:10:03.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:602164,603582}Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.70,0:10:07.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:605709,607628}No, that's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.62,0:10:11.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:607628,611215}It sounds almost like I'm waiting\Nfor bad things to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.34,0:10:18.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:613342,618305}But all in all, we have only two people.\NThat old man I just told you about,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.30,0:10:22.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:618305,622226}and Ms. Carraclough, a frail looking nurse\Nof tremendous willpower and endurance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.60,0:10:26.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:622601,626105}If something bad happens,\Nthere is nobody but us to deal with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.19,0:10:30.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:628190,630818}I've been losing sleep\Nat night thinking of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.81,0:10:32.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:630818,632611}I can't even take a proper nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.90,0:10:36.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:633904,636949}No, that's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.28,0:10:40.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:638284,640411}I love these moments.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.54,0:10:53.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:651547,653007}What's up, Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.00,0:10:53.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:653007,653841}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.84,0:10:55.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:653841,655426}It took it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.67,0:11:00.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:658679,660181}Good, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.47,0:11:03.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:662474,663017}And now…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.23,0:11:12.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:671233,672902}How's that, Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.90,0:11:14.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:672902,674320}This spot is the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.20,0:11:26.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:683204,686207}It's a pity that it got off the hook.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.75,0:11:31.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:687750,691128}But it was fun anyway.\NRight, Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.79,0:11:34.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:692796,694215}It was, it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.26,0:11:40.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:699261,700512}Hm? What's the matter?
Comment: 0,0:12:06.91,0:12:06.91,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:726914,726914}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.80,0:12:23.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:739802,743764}My leg got stuck under the rock…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.52,0:12:41.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:757528,761156}I appreciate your concern,\Nbut there is nothing you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.28,0:12:50.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:768289,770791}Let me think.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.51,0:13:09.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:787516,789059}Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.05,0:13:10.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:789059,790644}Where did she go?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.64,0:13:12.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:790644,792938}Maybe something happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.44,0:13:17.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:794440,797401}Maybe she's taking a nap\Nat home today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.49,0:13:27.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:805492,807536}Well, well!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.53,0:13:30.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:807536,810247}If it's not my favorite Lassie.\NWhat's up, doggie?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.71,0:13:36.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:814710,816795}I see, you're in good health.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.79,0:13:39.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:817796,819465}What are you doing, Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.68,0:13:51.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:830684,831977}Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.94,0:13:59.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:837941,839485}Lassie…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.53,0:14:11.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:848535,851747}Where did she disappear to?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.74,0:14:13.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:851747,853165}Maybe she's with Sandy's sheep!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.54,0:14:23.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:858545,863217}But even if she was playing at the pasture,\Nshe would come back to pick me up for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.34,0:14:32.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:868347,872226}Maybe she's still with Mom…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.27,0:14:43.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:881276,883320}She left ages ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.32,0:14:44.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:883320,884905}Didn't she come to pick you up?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.32,0:14:47.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:885322,887074}She didn't, which is\Nwhy I'm looking for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.11,0:14:49.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:888117,889952}Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.55,0:15:05.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:904550,905884}Hey, Smarty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.97,0:15:10.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:907970,910764}Did you see Lassie anywhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.15,0:15:24.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:924153,924987}Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.94,0:15:31.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:928949,931118}What is it, Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.11,0:15:35.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:931118,935038}What are you doing?\NLet go of my arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.20,0:15:39.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:938208,939835}What's up with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.58,0:15:42.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:940586,942421}You didn't come to school today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.29,0:15:46.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:943297,946008}Where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.00,0:15:47.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:946008,947426}Where were you playing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.55,0:15:54.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:953557,954975}Lassie? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.27,0:15:59.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:958270,959062}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.32,0:16:08.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:966320,968197}Wait, Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.11,0:16:11.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:970115,971575}Ah… Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.09,0:16:33.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:992095,993847}Dr. Hopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.68,0:16:37.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:995682,997351}John?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.93,0:16:39.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:997935,999728}Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.72,0:16:40.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:999728,1000979}Dr. Hopper.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.31,0:16:43.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1002314,1003982}This is embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.98,0:16:46.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1003982,1006610}A rock fell on my leg and\NI cannot move, as you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.49,0:16:56.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1013492,1016745}It's no use.\NIt won't budge…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.12,0:17:03.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1022125,1023293}Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.29,0:17:06.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1023293,1026171}Bring someone here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.63,0:17:10.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1028632,1030008}I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.26,0:17:21.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1038267,1041103}Lassie, take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.10,0:17:24.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1041103,1044565}Doesn't matter who, just show it\Nto the first person you meet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.56,0:17:27.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1044565,1047568}Did you understand?\NThe first person you meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.53,0:17:42.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1059538,1062040}Doctor, it'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.04,0:17:45.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1062040,1065252}Lassie will bring\Nsomeone here soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.67,0:17:48.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1066670,1068630}I'm sorry, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.02,0:18:04.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1083020,1084479}It's you, Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.94,0:18:08.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1086940,1088400}How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.98,0:18:13.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1090986,1093655}Okay, girl.\NWhat brings you here today?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.65,0:18:14.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1093655,1094489}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.03,0:18:22.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1100037,1102998}Oh dear. What's this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.08,0:18:27.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1105083,1107044}What's going on, Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.04,0:18:29.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1107044,1109379}It's a handkerchief…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.37,0:18:31.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1109379,1111048}It's John's?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.04,0:18:32.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1111048,1112591}Hm? "SOS".
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.59,0:18:35.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1112591,1115135}Ah! John's in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.77,0:18:50.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1128774,1130067}What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.98,0:18:56.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1132986,1136657}John wrote he's near the log bridge,\Nbut I have no idea where it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.65,0:18:57.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1136657,1137991}Does any of you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.99,0:18:59.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1137991,1139660}The log bridge?\NDoesn't ring a bell…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.54,0:19:14.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1152547,1154841}How much longer, Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.96,0:19:19.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1156968,1159596}How far did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.26,0:19:25.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1160263,1165936}I'm sorry I dragged you\Ninto this, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.93,0:19:28.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1165936,1168146}Don't be silly, sir.\NAre you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.14,0:19:29.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1168146,1169439}Yes, somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.43,0:19:34.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1169439,1174027}But if Lassie weren't here with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.02,0:19:37.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1174027,1177322}no one would look for me\Nin this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.32,0:19:41.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1177322,1181493}I would have to wait\Nuntil someone passed by.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.45,0:19:46.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1183453,1186623}It frightens me thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.62,0:19:49.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1187624,1189459}She's incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.83,0:19:55.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1191837,1195132}John, did you hear\Nanything just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.88,0:20:02.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1201888,1202723}Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.22,0:20:05.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1204224,1205684}Why did you stop, Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.68,0:20:06.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1205684,1206768}The bridge collapsed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.76,0:20:07.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1206768,1207644}Look, there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.64,0:20:09.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1207644,1209896}John! Dr. Hopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.89,0:20:12.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1209896,1212232}Doctor, help arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.23,0:20:15.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1212232,1215193}Lassie went to get Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.19,0:20:16.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1215193,1216528}That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.82,0:20:21.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1218822,1221074}Hang in there, John!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.07,0:20:23.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1221074,1223452}We're on our way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.41,0:20:25.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1224411,1225954}We'll rescue you in a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.95,0:20:26.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1225954,1226955}Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.95,0:20:28.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1226955,1228540}Good job, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.20,0:20:31.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1230208,1231543}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.62,0:20:36.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1233628,1236548}Knock it off, Lassie.\NIt tickles!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.25,0:20:39.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1237257,1239050}Come on, Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.05,0:20:40.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1239050,1240594}John…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.59,0:20:42.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1240594,1242095}Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.09,0:20:44.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1242095,1244014}Lassie is so smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.01,0:20:46.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1244014,1246099}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.06,0:20:58.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1257068,1258737}Take care of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.86,0:21:07.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1263867,1267788}Doctor, that was\Nthe last patient for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.24,0:21:11.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1268246,1271124}You saved me, both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.12,0:21:12.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1271124,1272793}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.54,0:21:20.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1275545,1280842}Even such an old and decrepit doctor\Nseems to be useful for something.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.84,0:21:23.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1280842,1283678}I'm glad it ended with only this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.67,0:21:27.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1283678,1287808}They say a friend in need\Nis a friend indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.80,0:21:33.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1287808,1293063}Lassie, you showed today\Nthat you're a very precious friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.77,0:21:37.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1293772,1297609}Next time we'll catch\Neven bigger fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.60,0:21:38.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1297609,1298902}Doctor…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.90,0:21:43.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1298902,1303073}I'd like to remind you that you need\Nto fully heal before going anywhere.
